   "text": "skills create <name> --owner <team>\n\nskills generate <name>\n  --description \"...\"\n  --owner travel-platform\n  \u2514\u2500 Gemini 2.5 Flash \u2192 SKILL.md body\n  \u2514\u2500 registers in registry.yaml (draft)\n\nskills validate --all\n\nskills package <name>\n  \u2192 releases/<name>/<v>/skill.zip\n\nskills list / info / delete",
