   "locked": false,
   "text": "Travel Agent  (agent/travel_agent.py)\nLangGraph + LangChain\n\nsystem_prompt = harness_config base_system_prompt\n  + skill.body  (or no skill for baseline)\nharness_config.yaml externalized; HARNESS_CONFIG_PATH\n  env override for candidate configs\n\nTools (9):\n  search_flights \u00b7 search_hotels \u00b7 create_booking\n  modify_booking \u00b7 cancel_booking \u00b7 get_fare_rules\n  check_availability \u00b7 validate_passenger \u00b7 get_itinerary\n\nModel: gpt-4o-mini (default) \u00b7 --model for others\nagent_mode=orchestrated \u2192 Phase 8 specialists",
   "fontSize": 13,
   "fontFamily": 2,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 13,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "Travel Agent  (agent/travel_agent.py)\nLangGraph + LangChain\n\nsystem_prompt = harness_config base_system_prompt\n  + skill.body  (or no skill for baseline)\nharness_config.yaml externalized; HARNESS_CONFIG_PATH\n  env override for candidate configs\n\nTools (9):\n  search_flights \u00b7 search_hotels \u00b7 create_booking\n  modify_booking \u00b7 cancel_booking \u00b7 get_fare_rules\n  check_availability \u00b7 validate_passenger \u00b7 get_itinerary\n\nModel: gpt-4o-mini (default) \u00b7 --model for others\nagent_mode=orchestrated \u2192 Phase 8 specialists",
