   "isDeleted": false,
   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "Gate Check  (eval/gate_check.py)\n\nweighted_delta = \u03a3(delta \u00d7 weight) / \u03a3w\nDomain weights: booking=3.0 flight/hotel=2.0\n\nThresholds calibrated for N=3 trials:\nT1 BLOCK   w\u0394<\u22120.15 | crit<\u22120.30 | reg>50%  exit(1)\nT2 SOFT    w\u0394<\u22120.05 | heavy<\u22120.20 | reg>35%  exit(1)\nT3 WARN    small regressions              exit(0)",
   "fontSize": 13,
   "fontFamily": 2,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 13,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "Gate Check  (eval/gate_check.py)\n\nweighted_delta = \u03a3(delta \u00d7 weight) / \u03a3w\nDomain weights: booking=3.0 flight/hotel=2.0\n\nThresholds calibrated for N=3 trials:\nT1 BLOCK   w\u0394<\u22120.15 | crit<\u22120.30 | reg>50%  exit(1)\nT2 SOFT    w\u0394<\u22120.05 | heavy<\u22120.20 | reg>35%  exit(1)\nT3 WARN    small regressions              exit(0)",
