   "text": "LangSmith  (smith.langchain.com)  \u2014 replaced Langfuse\n\nFull LLM call tree per run, tool spans\nTraces tagged: skill / condition / domain\nTrace URL stored in EvalResult\n\u2192 surfaced in PR comment for regressions\n\nKeys: LANGSMITH_API_KEY / LANGSMITH_PROJECT\n\u26a0 monthly trace quota can hit 429 \u2014 disable via\n  LANGCHAIN_TRACING_V2=false",
   "fontSize": 13,
   "fontFamily": 2,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 13,
