   "text": "SQLite Trajectory Store  (trajectory.db)\nLightweight local supplement to Langfuse\n\nruns table: task_id, condition, score, failure_mode\nsteps table: tool_name, latency_ms, tokens\n\n7 failure modes:\n  NO_TOOL_CALL  WRONG_TOOL  MISSING_PARAM\n  MULTI_STEP_DROPOUT  PARTIAL_MATCH\n  HALLUCINATED_ID  UNKNOWN\n\n\u2192 feeds GRPO propose_skill clustering",
