   "locked": false,
   "text": "Optimizer Stack  (eval/optimizer/)\n\noptimize.py \u2014 two-target ReflACT trainer (Slice 3)\n  failure_classification.json \u2192 SKILL.md body OR one\n  harness_config key \u00b7 5:3:2 split \u00b7 mixed gate\n  propose-only: *_proposed.* + optimization_report.json\n\narchive.py + bandit.py (Slice 4) \u2014 Thompson sampling\n  over 5 edit strategies (--explore)\n\npropose_skill.py \u2014 auto-PR for missing skills\n  branch proposal/<name> \u2014 NEVER auto-merged",
   "fontSize": 13,
   "fontFamily": 2,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 13,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "Optimizer Stack  (eval/optimizer/)\n\noptimize.py \u2014 two-target ReflACT trainer (Slice 3)\n  failure_classification.json \u2192 SKILL.md body OR one\n  harness_config key \u00b7 5:3:2 split \u00b7 mixed gate\n  propose-only: *_proposed.* + optimization_report.json\n\narchive.py + bandit.py (Slice 4) \u2014 Thompson sampling\n  over 5 edit strategies (--explore)\n\npropose_skill.py \u2014 auto-PR for missing skills\n  branch proposal/<name> \u2014 NEVER auto-merged",
   "lineHeight": 1.4
