  {
   "id": "t_path_a",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 2848,
   "y": 92,
   "width": 964,
   "height": 796,
   "angle": 0,
   "strokeColor": "#374151",
   "backgroundColor": "transparent",
   "fillStyle": "solid",
   "strokeWidth": 1,
   "strokeStyle": "solid",
   "roughness": 0,
   "opacity": 100,
   "roundness": null,
   "groupIds": [],
   "frameId": null,
   "boundElements": [],
   "seed": 50,
   "version": 1,
   "versionNonce": 1,
   "isDeleted": false,
   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "PATH A \u2014 skills generate\n(human-initiated, LLM-drafted)\n\n$ skills generate disruption-handling \\\n    --description \"Handle cancelled flights\n    and rebooking\" \\\n    --owner travel-platform\n\nFlow:\n1. validate name (VALID_SKILL_NAME regex)\n2. call Gemini 2.5 Flash via OpenRouter\n   GENERATE_PROMPT:\n     name + description \u2192\n     structured SKILL.md body\n     (Workflow, Inputs, Output,\n      Edge Cases)\n3. build YAML frontmatter\n4. write skills/<name>/SKILL.md\n5. upsert registry.yaml (status: draft)\n\nOutput:\n\"Generated skill: skills/disruption-handling\nReview SKILL.md before opening a PR\"\n\nHuman reviews + edits\n\u2192 opens PR\n\u2192 CI eval gate runs\n\u2192 PASS / BLOCK",
   "fontSize": 13,
   "fontFamily": 2,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 13,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "",
   "lineHeight": 1.4
  },
