   "frameId": null,
   "boundElements": [],
   "seed": 52,
   "version": 1,
   "versionNonce": 1,
   "isDeleted": false,
   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "PATH B \u2014 GRPO auto-proposal\n(system-initiated, from failures)\n\n$ python -m eval.optimizer.propose_skill \\\n    --threshold 5 \\\n    --github-token ghp_... \\\n    --repo Tabhi-Commons/travel-agent-skills\n\nFlow:\n1. load_failure_clusters(trajectory.db)\n   OR load_clusters_from_ab_results()\n2. skip domains with existing skill\n3. group by domain + failure_mode\n   require >= threshold (default 5)\n4. draft_skill_body() \n   Gemini 2.5 Flash:\n   failure context \u2192 SKILL.md body\n5. open_skill_pr() via GitHub API\n   branch: proposal/<skill-name>\n   commit: skills/<name>/SKILL.md\n   PR title: \"proposal: auto-generated <name>\"\n6. CI eval gate runs automatically on PR\n7. Human reviews content\n   approves or closes\n   NEVER auto-merged\n\n--dry-run flag: print proposals, no PR",
   "fontSize": 13,
   "fontFamily": 2,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 13,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "",
   "lineHeight": 1.4
  },
