   "text": "\ud83d\udd11  Models \u2014 eval default: gpt-4o-mini (OPENAI_API_KEY direct)\nOptimizer-side LLM: gpt-4o \u00b7 others via OpenRouter (openrouter.ai/api/v1)\n\nUsed by: Travel Agent \u00b7 LLM Judge \u00b7 Optimizer \u00b7 propose_skill \u00b7 skills generate \u00b7 taskgen\nPer-model leaderboard: model recorded in every ab_results.json",
   "fontSize": 14,
